<div class="landing-page-container">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-custom navbar-fixed-top" role="navigation">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-header">
                <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-main-collapse">
                    <i class="fa fa-bars"></i>
                </button>
                <a class="navbar-brand page-scroll" href="#page-top">
                  <span class="light">Oogway's List</span>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse navbar-right navbar-main-collapse">

              <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                    <li style="position:relative; top:6px;">
                        <a class="page-scroll" href="#download">Sign Up</a>
                    </li>

                </ul>
                <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: session_path(resource_name), html: {class: "navbar-form navbar-left"}) do |f| %>

                  <div class="form-group">
                    <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, class: "form-control" %>
                  </div>

                  <div class="form-group">
                    <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off", class: "form-control" %>
                  </div>

                  <div class="form-group">
                    <%= f.submit "Log in", class: "btn btn-oogway" %>
                  </div>
                <% end %>

            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="intro">
        <div class="intro-body">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                        <h1 class="brand-heading">Oogway's List</h1>
                        <p class="intro-text">A way to organize the movies you want to watch with your friends.</p>
                        <a href="#about" class="btn-circle page-scroll" style="display: inline-block">
                            <i class="fa fa-angle-double-down animated"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="about" class="container content-section text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                <h2>About Oogway's List</h2>
                <p>This is a place where you can keep track of all of those movies you wanted to watch. And who you wanted to watch them with. </p>

                <p>This is also a place that will tell you what to watch once you’ve told it how much you liked watching what you've watched and how much you think you’d like to watch what you haven’t.</p>

                <p>“One often meets his destiny on the road he takes to avoid it.”</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="download" class="content-section text-center">
        <div class="download-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                    <h2>Sign Up For Oogway's List</h2>
                    <p>You can sign up with just your email, via facebook or google+.</p>

                    <ul class="list-inline banner-social-buttons">
                        <li>
                            <a href="/users/sign_up" class="btn btn-oogway btn-lg"><i class="fa fa-envelope fa-fw"></i> <span class="network-name">With Email</span></a>

                        </li>
                        <li>
                        <li>
                            <button href="#" class="btn btn-oogway btn-lg" disabled><i class="fa fa-facebook fa-fw"></i> <span class="network-name">With Facebook</span></button>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <button href="#" class="btn btn-oogway btn-lg" disabled><i class="fa fa-google-plus fa-fw"></i> <span class="network-name">With Google+</span></button>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="container content-section text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                <h2>Contact Oogway</h2>
                <p>Feel free to email us to provide some feedback on our list, give me suggestions for new functions, or to just say hello!</p>
                <p><a href="mailto:feedback@startbootstrap.com" class="dark-link">feedback@oogwayslist.com</a>
                </p>
                <ul class="list-inline banner-social-buttons">
                    <li>
                        <button href="#" class="btn btn-oogway btn-lg" disabled><i class="fa fa-twitter fa-fw"></i> <span class="network-name">Twitter</span></button>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="https://github.com/danarmstrong-io/group_movie_queue" class="btn btn-oogway btn-lg"><i class="fa fa-github fa-fw"></i> <span class="network-name">Github</span></a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <button href="#" class="btn btn-oogway btn-lg" disabled><i class="fa fa-google-plus fa-fw"></i> <span class="network-name">Google+</span></button>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container text-center">
            <p>Copyright &copy; Oogway's List 2015</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>

